      <div align="Left">
<!---------------------------->
<table cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Recommended Level<br>for starting quest:</b></td><td valign="bottom"> 45<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting zone:</b></td><td valign="top"> Kael Drakkal<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Additional zones:</b></td><td valign="top"> Eastern Wastes<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting NPC:</b></td><td valign="top"> Clrakk Blackfist<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Reward:</b></td><td valign="top"> Dark Spear of Venom<br><br></td></tr>
</table>

Depending on which body part you turn in, you will get either the Dark Spear of Venom or the Mask of Malediction.<br>
<br>
Clrakk Blackfist in Kael Drakkal has a particular hatred for the Coldain (as should everyone).  If you talk to him at length he will request you to "bring them strife".  To do so, he asks that you kill Deaen Greyforge, the Coldain.<br>
<br>
Deaen is about level 45 and a paladin, the perfect enemy for any respectable Shadow Knight.  He can be found at a dwarf camp near the Ry'Gorr fort where Garadain Glacierbane resides.  The location is approximately -2600, -400.<br>
<br>
He spawns about once or twice a day (if killed) but is rarely hunted.  To get him, you will either need to harmony the four dwarves by the fire and Garadain, or kill them first.  Deaen will heal himself and Lay on Hands when injured so you could be in for a long fight.  I wouldn't suggest trying to solo him until you're in your low 50s, but with a competent partner, you should be able to take him out at 45.<br>
When killed he will either drop his hand or his leg.<br>
<br>
Return his hand to Clrakk Blackfist for the Mask of Malediction:<Br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM  <br>
Wis: -4 Int: +5 Fire Resist: -5 Cold Resist: -5 Mana: +10  <br>
Weight: 0.2 <br>
Classes: All Classes  <br>
Races: All Races  <br>
Inventory Slot: Face<br>
<br>
Return his leg to Clrakk Blackfist for the Dark Spear of Venom:<br>
MAGIC ITEM NO DROP  <br>
Damage: 17<br>
Delay: 27 <br>
Ratio: 1.588 Amazing <br>
Int: +5 Magic Resist: +5 HP: +20  <br>
Weight: 7.0 <br>
Weapon Skill: Piercing <br>
Classes: Shadowknight  <br>
Races: All Races  <br>
Inventory Slot: Primary or Range <br>
<br>
Killing Clrakk Blackfist will sometimes result in him dropping the Mask or Spear.<br>

